title: Bobby Meeting His Girlfriend’s Parents + Dr. Fauci Joins Us + Bobby’s Mailbag: Breaking Up Over Zoom
itunes:title: Bobby Meeting His Girlfriend’s Parents + Dr. Fauci Joins Us + Bobby’s Mailbag: Breaking Up Over Zoom
description:
Bobby gives an honest update about him and his girlfriend Caitlin hitting the 5-week mark together in quarantine. Bobby shares that he'll be going to meet up with her family next Friday. Bobby talks to Dr. Fauci about when concerts will return, changes we'll see in restaurants and how we can protect ourselves in public. Plus, Bobby opens up the mailbag from a guy who wants to break up with his girlfriend over Zoom!
